des: "The best cranberry sauce you will ever taste. Many spices make this delightful sauce the hit of any occasion."
ins: Bring cranberries, white sugar, brown sugar, water, cinnamon, ginger, cloves, and allspice  to a boil over medium-high heat in a large saucepan; cook and stir for 20 minutes. Stir in apple; cook and stir until apple is tender and sauce is thick, about 5 minutes. Refrigerate until cold.
